<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="2">념녀던</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09b" n="1">받긔 오 아이 됴오니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09b" n="2">긷거</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09b" n="3">그러오나</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10a" n="1">東萊 려오신 젼의 위션 封進物을 바드려 야</sent>

